    <briefdescription>
<para>A passkey used to establish a parent-child relationship between a <ref refid="classhelios_1_1rendering_1_1RenderTarget" kindref="compound">RenderTarget</ref> and a <ref refid="classhelios_1_1rendering_1_1Viewport" kindref="compound">Viewport</ref>. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This struct uses the passkey idiom to restrict the calling of `Viewport::setRenderTarget` to friend classes (specifically `helios::rendering::RenderTarget`), ensuring that the ownership hierarchy is managed correctly.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para>`Viewport::setRenderTarget` </para>
